Live Hog futures were expected to opensteady to mostly higher after yesterday's mostly higher close.    Traders anticipate carryover demand prompted by firmer livecalls and the continued discount of futures to cash. Hog runsare light as farmers are starting spring fieldwork in someareas, they noted.    Private reports of steady to firm cash pork products and arise in the cutout yesterday was adding to packer interest forcash hogs, they said.    Spillover strength from higher cattle pits is also likelyagain today, they added. Reuter&#3;